h4. Purpose

There are times when Weceem must return feedback to users, for example when returning search results or after submitting content.

This tag will allow you to insert Weceem's UI message anywhere in your page as appropriate.

*Example*

{code}
<wcm:uiMessage>
    <div class="info-message">
        ${message.encodeAsHTML()}
    </div>
</wcm:uiMessage> 
{code}

